    "SlateportCity_PokemonFanClub_Text_GiveMonMorePokeblocks": "Hmmm… It's not bad, but it's not\\ngood, either…\\pYou, the TRAINER, must put more\\neffort into raising this POKéMON!\\pFor instance, may I suggest that\\nyou give it more {POKEBLOCK}S?",
