    "SlateportCity_PokemonFanClub_Text_MonMostImpressiveGiveItThis": "Your {STR_VAR_1}, it is growing in\\na most impressive manner!\\lIt is one fine specimen!\\pBut! If you were to give it this,\\nit would grow even better! Indeed!",
