    "SlateportCity_PokemonFanClub_Text_ShowMePokemonThatLoveYou": "I love seeing POKéMON that love\\ntheir TRAINERS.\\pPOKéMON are very sensitive to\\nthe feelings of their TRAINERS.\\pIf you treat your POKéMON with love\\nand care, they'll love you back.\\pWhen your POKéMON grow to love you,\\nplease come show me.",
